2. Batch Processing

Send events in batches to reduce network overhead:

const eventBatch = [];
const flushBatch = () => {
if (eventBatch.length > 0) {
sendBatch(eventBatch);
eventBatch.length = 0;
}
};
setInterval(flushBatch, 1000); // Flush every second

